    <entry>
      <title>查询序列元素(链表)</title>
      <link href="2021/06/16/OJ_Link/"/>
      <url>2021/06/16/OJ_Link/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="OJ链表练习之查询序列元素"><a href="#OJ链表练习之查询序列元素" class="headerlink" title="OJ链表练习之查询序列元素"></a>OJ链表练习之查询序列元素</h1><p><strong>问题描述:</strong><br>使用带头结点的单链表编程：一群学生排成一行，输入一个学号，请确定该学号学生所在的位置。</p><p><strong>输入说明:</strong><br>第一行输入学生信息：第一个整数n(0&lt;=n&lt;=100)，表示共有n个学生，其后有n个整数，表示n个学生的学号。<br>第二行及以后各行，每行输入一个整数，表示要查找的学生学号。</p><p><strong>输出说明:</strong><br>对于每个要查找的学号，输出一个整数，表示要查找学生的位置。如果共有n个学生，则位置序号为1~n。<br>如果学生不存在，输出“no”，不包括双引号。每个输出占一行。</p><p><strong>输入范例:</strong><br>12 50 51 52 53 54 49 4 5 10 11 9 12<br>50<br>11<br>12<br>3</p><p><strong>输出范例：</strong><br>1<br>10<br>12<br>no</p><h2 id="结点的定义"><a href="#结点的定义" class="headerlink" title="结点的定义"></a>结点的定义</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">#include &lt;iostream&gt;</span><br><span class="line">using namespace std;</span><br><span class="line">//定义结点</span><br><span class="line">struct ListNode&#123;</span><br><span class="line">int val; //结点数据域</span><br><span class="line">struct ListNode *next; //结点的next指针</span><br><span class="line">&#125;;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="根据题意-需要用尾插法创建链表"><a href="#根据题意-需要用尾插法创建链表" class="headerlink" title="根据题意,需要用尾插法创建链表"></a>根据题意,需要用<code>尾插法</code>创建链表</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ListNode *createByTail()</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    ListNode *head;</span><br><span class="line">    ListNode *p1,*p2;</span><br><span class="line">    int num,val;</span><br><span class="line">    cin&gt;&gt;num;</span><br><span class="line">    if(num == 0)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        head == NULL;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;else&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        int i = 0;</span><br><span class="line">        head=NULL;  //首先置链表为空链表</span><br><span class="line">        while(i&lt;num)</span><br><span class="line">        &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            cin&gt;&gt;val;</span><br><span class="line">            p1=new ListNode;</span><br><span class="line">            p1-&gt;val=val;</span><br><span class="line">            i=i+1;</span><br><span class="line">            if(i==1)       //创建第一个结点</span><br><span class="line">                head=p1;</span><br><span class="line">            else</span><br><span class="line">                p2-&gt;next=p1;</span><br><span class="line">            p2=p1;   //p2始终指向最后一个结点（即尾指针）</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        p2-&gt;next=NULL;  //切记：最后一个结点的next赋值为NULL</span><br><span class="line">        return head;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>这里需要判断num是否为0的情况，否则一开始的链表就为空的话就不会输出head–&gt;tail，而会直接退出程序。</p></blockquote><h2 id="根据特定值查找对应结点并返回其位置-从1开始"><a href="#根据特定值查找对应结点并返回其位置-从1开始" class="headerlink" title="根据特定值查找对应结点并返回其位置(从1开始)"></a>根据特定值查找对应结点并返回其位置<code>(从1开始)</code></h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">//寻找当前元素位置，没有则返回0</span><br><span class="line">int Locate(ListNode *head,int val)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">int count=1;</span><br><span class="line">    ListNode *p;</span><br><span class="line">p=head;</span><br><span class="line">while(p)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">if (p-&gt;val==val)</span><br><span class="line">        &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            break;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">p=p-&gt;next;</span><br><span class="line">count++;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">if(p==NULL)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">return 0;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;else&#123;</span><br><span class="line">return count;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="main函数"><a href="#main函数" class="headerlink" title="main函数"></a>main函数</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">int main()</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    ListNode *head;</span><br><span class="line">head=createByTail();</span><br><span class="line">int val;</span><br><span class="line">while(cin&gt;&gt;val)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">int locate = Locate(head,val);</span><br><span class="line">if(locate==0)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">cout&lt;&lt;&quot;no&quot;&lt;&lt;endl;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;else&#123;</span><br><span class="line">cout&lt;&lt;locate&lt;&lt;endl;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">return 0;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
